We never really get out of depression. We just learn to cope. 

We learn to live with it. 
We learn to supress it. 

That's why we do everything to keep from being in our own heads. 

Fall asleep, before falling apart. 
It gets easier.

#depression #MentalHealthAwarenessWeek
